  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/a6fb7e1f58b0e301ceecc7c25683cee0.avif?t=1683298837\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><strong>HatLand</strong> is a game where you need to see <strong>GAME OVER</strong> many times to complete a level. But each time, passing further along the inner corridors of the Empire's spaceships, you will become stronger...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/12ce269e7e2add82f1d6377a3fb7008a.poster.avif?t=1683298837\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/12ce269e7e2add82f1d6377a3fb7008a.webm?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/12ce269e7e2add82f1d6377a3fb7008a.mp4?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2>— Melee and ranged enemy mechanics, allowing you to dodge and avoid taking damage at the right moment!<br>— Traps, mines, TNT - everything that you can turn at the right moment against opponents!<br>— A system of items and improvements, bundles of which will help you get to the next room.<br>— 9 unique bosses!<br>— 10 different types of enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/42931fffa7553e5089920be446acc6cd.poster.avif?t=1683298837\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/42931fffa7553e5089920be446acc6cd.webm?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/42931fffa7553e5089920be446acc6cd.mp4?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/a6fb7e1f58b0e301ceecc7c25683cee0.avif?t=1683298837\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><strong>HatLand</strong> is a game where you need to see <strong>GAME OVER</strong> many times to complete a level. But each time, passing further along the inner corridors of the Empire's spaceships, you will become stronger...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/12ce269e7e2add82f1d6377a3fb7008a.poster.avif?t=1683298837\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/12ce269e7e2add82f1d6377a3fb7008a.webm?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/12ce269e7e2add82f1d6377a3fb7008a.mp4?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2>— Melee and ranged enemy mechanics, allowing you to dodge and avoid taking damage at the right moment!<br>— Traps, mines, TNT - everything that you can turn at the right moment against opponents!<br>— A system of items and improvements, bundles of which will help you get to the next room.<br>— 9 unique bosses!<br>— 10 different types of enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/42931fffa7553e5089920be446acc6cd.poster.avif?t=1683298837\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/42931fffa7553e5089920be446acc6cd.webm?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388480/extras/42931fffa7553e5089920be446acc6cd.mp4?t=1683298837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
